<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <% include ./partials/head.ejs %>
    </head>
    <body>

        <!-- Navigation -->
        <% include ./partials/navbar.ejs %>
        <% include ../static/partials/messages.ejs %>

        <!-- Page Content -->
        <main class="container-fluid">

            <div id="mainHeader" class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-12 text-center">
                    <h1 class="display-1">Welcome to Blocipedia!</h1>
                    <p class="lead">
                        This is Blocipedia, the premier knowledge hub of the web. Come join a large open-source community dedicated towards the transfer of information.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Jumbotron Header -->
            <header id="mainJumbo" class="jumbotron my-4">
                <% if(currentUser){ %>
                    <p class="h3">Hello <%= currentUser.username %>!</p>
                    <% if(currentUser.role === 0) { %>
                        <p class="lead">Want to be able to create private wikis? Click below to upgrade your account!</p>
                        <form action="users/<%= currentUser.id %>/upgrade" method="POST">
                            <script
                                src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button"
                                data-key="pk_test_SzCvbipJ9yfY4isz80dsfHoV"
                                data-amount="1500"
                                data-name="Blocipedia"
                                data-description="Upgrade Account to Premium"
                                data-image="https://stripe.com/img/documentation/checkout/marketplace.png"
                                data-locale="auto">
                            </script>
                        </form>
                    <% } else if(currentUser.role === 1) { %>
                        <p class="lead">Click below to downgrade your account from premiun to standard</p>
                        <a href="/users/<%= currentUser.id %>/downgrade" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Downgrade</a>
                    <% } %>
                <% } else if(!currentUser) { %>
                    <p class="h3">Want to drop some knowledge?</p>
                    <p class="lead">Sign up for a free account and share what you know!</p>
                    <a href="/users/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Sign up</a>
                <% } %>
            </header>

            <!-- Page Features -->
            <div id="featured" class="container-fluid">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-9">
                        <h1 class="display-4">Featured Wiki</h1>
                        <div class="card border-dark mb-1">
                            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://www.riotgames.com/darkroom/1440/9963d4c630b7e7865695d5f8800c1538:a7196d2d2f12d4eae709a3d15f1cbf46/.jfif" alt="Card image cap">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h1 class="card-title display-3">Seoul</h5>
                                <hr>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    <h2>Lorem Ipsum</h2>
                                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. In non sem et tellus semper vulputate eu nec libero. Cras mi ante, ullamcorper nec enim eget, venenatis aliquet leo. Sed congue erat sodales commodo mollis. Pellentesque sit amet porttitor ipsum. Donec tellus ex, pretium id augue commodo, tempor ultricies velit. Nam mi justo, tincidunt vitae massa ac, consectetur ullamcorper ex. Nullam molestie nec nunc vitae tincidunt. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Aenean egestas mattis nunc, eget blandit ligula. Maecenas elit lacus, pellentesque ut velit id, viverra bibendum dolor. Praesent porttitor varius nunc sed imperdiet. Curabitur et lacinia purus. Sed vitae arcu interdum, mattis urna vel, malesuada lectus. Integer vitae quam ut odio faucibus feugiat in quis tellus. Donec cursus metus purus, iaculis pretium erat consectetur eu. In hac habitasse platea dictumst.</p>
                                </p>
                                <h1><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h"></i></h1>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">View Full Wiki</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-3">
                        <h1 class="display-4">About Us</h1>
                        <div id="aboutUs" class="list-group text-center">
                            <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start border border-dark">
                                <h5 class="mb-1">Connect</h5>
                                <h1><i class="fas fa-link"></i></h1>
                                <p class="mb-1">A premier source for user-generated content. Connect, share, and learn about any topic. If you don't find it, add it and share your knowledge with the world.</p>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Join Today</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start border border-dark">
                                <h5 class="mb-1">Share</h5>
                                <h1><i class="fas fa-comments"></i></h1>
                                <p class="mb-1">Share your knowledge with the community by creating your own Wiki. Have full control over how your wiki looks by using markdown syntax.</p>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Create A Wiki</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start border border-dark">
                                <h5 class="mb-1">Collaborate</h5>
                                <h1><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i></h1>
                                <p class="mb-1">Work with other members from around the world to have the most complete Wiki possible. We allow you to edit and have control over content as a Wiki Admin.</p>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Premium Content</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start border border-dark">
                                <h5 class="mb-1">Protect</h5>
                                <h1><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></h1>
                                <p class="mb-1">Premium Users have access to private wikis that only they can see. You can choose who you would like to share with and who can contribute content as a Premium User.</p>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start border border-dark">
                                <h5 class="mb-1">Learn</h5>
                                <h1><i class="fas fa-chalkboard"></i></h1>
                                <p class="mb-1">With users from around the world sharing their knowledge, there is no limit to what you can learn. From Aa to Zoology, you are free to learn what you want, when you want. It is only a click away.</p>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Start Exploring</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <!-- <% include ./partials/footer.ejs %> -->

        <% include ./partials/baseScripts.ejs %>
    </body>
</html>